reviewText: I love D.L. Hughley.  I have seen him in person so this DVD is like I am watching him live again.
Excellent!  It was awesome. I have recommended this to friends.

"Clear" is the follow-up to DL's "Reset" comedy special, and like it, it's funny from start to finish. DL's take on pop culture, politics, and his family life is hilarious! It's a great add to your stand up comedy collection.
IT'S D.L HUGHLEY! GUARANTEED TO BE FUNNY!
Very funny, a legend of comedy always brings out the laughter in you and the tears do flow.... Must watch!
This is definitely the funny side of life.  Recommend it.
I enjoy DL Hughley's sense of humor.
Product rec'd in new condition.  I njoyed this dvd.
